d speak up in support of what could be a fun additional form of combat for the thief who sometimes prefers not to bloody his hands to get the gold <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
